    "The majority of existing research primarily concentrates on detecting the authenticity of content while disregarding the underlying intent or purpose behind the content.",
    "In general, false information is often created with the specific intention of deceiving audiences.",
    "Occasionally, false information may take the form of satire and be published without any malicious intent.",
    "Therefore, a more precise classification of information which is done based on intent, can be particularly effective in identifying misinformation from disinformation.",
